senate republicans are seeking to grab the 
initiative on campaign finance reform with a proposal to ban all 
political action committees but set no overall spending limits 
republican leaders on tuesday unveiled a package supported by 34 
of the senates 45 gop members as democrats continued haggling 
behind closed doors on their proposal 
