vegas in the 1960s and 70s blending popular standards and 
operatic arias 
he made 25 albums including such songs as o sole mio 
wind beneath my wings and memory in the mid1970s franchi 
crooned volare ohhhhhhhh in commercials for the volare 
automobile 
born in cremona italy franchi studied to be an engineer while 
training in opera he performed in south africa in la traviata 
la boheme and carmen before leaving to advance his operatic 
career 
in italy england and later the united states he encountered 
difficulty getting parts instead he became a frequent guest on 
the ed sullivan show 
his film credits included a supporting role in the secret of 
santa vittoria in 1969 
survivors include his wife eva a daughter a son and two 
sisters 
funeral services will be private 
