to iranian control about 6 billion of that was used by iran to 
pay western bank loans 
the amount of iranian funds still frozen in accounts runs only 
into the millions the tribunal source said 
the tribunal is seeking a way to settle the small claims 
together and wipe out the remaining caseload of 2450 
