makes food offerings to pele daily his store has been spared on 
several previous flows 
let her take it if she wants it said yamaguchi 82 she 
can do what she wants its hers if she wants it 
even gov john waihee who toured the area tuesday said the 
fate of kalapana is in peles hands 
nobody can tell madame pele when it all ends the governor 
said nobody can tell her what to do 
legend also says pele gets upset when people try to run away 
from her and that she will find and destroy them 
this doesnt seem to scare officials at star of the sea church 
workers are preparing to relocate the renowned painted church 
from destruction 
not all in the congregation want to move the church they say it 
shows a lack of faith by the congregation and a lack of respect for 
pele 
