where the anticipated event had been a showdown with hostile suitor 
torchmark corp 
harold s hook american generals chairman said the company 
decided to put itself up for auction because it was vulnerable to a 
possible takeover at a discount price and wanted to realize the 
maximum value for its stockholders 
american general finished up 750 at 4762 a share as the 
